{"tid":625252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選毒撚最中意出沒食野地方","createTime":"2018-04-11T09:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T15:14:14.000Z","uid":180913,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9806a8cd0c6abed181638b2f389132fcac0526","tid":625252,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"毒撚地方應該人少少 要夠安靜 仲要無心理壓力迫你走等你可以坐長時間<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n元氣，係2點30至6點都唔會有人趕你走，成日食個tea都係50蚊起，仲有無限 綠茶同埋人少少，人少少感覺好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，上下連登同 睇下書溫下notes飲啖熱茶好爽<br />\n<br />\n一人唱k 連自助餐 我記得6點起去到3 4點都唔趕<br />\n都係200蚊埋單<br />\n個時neway同加州紅 鬥得最勁 學生去早唱40蚊埋單<br />\n差唔多個個星期去k房拎哂成堆食物大字形訓起度一路食野一路諗野<br />\n唱通宵就好扮去同學屋企其實係k房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nm記個d太嘈 好多人冷靜唔到落黎思考<br />\n<br />\n而加食緊元氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/174644_4ac01dca2c4c395866864b647c3c1f15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F174644_4ac01dca2c4c395866864b647c3c1f15.jpg&h=959a06bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19306cd40911a5ae8b4787c9c5d22ba2cef63b75","tid":625252,"uid":87688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"發霉定中毒"},{"pid":"74e4b53e28c4a958c050566c038c3dbe32bd1227","tid":625252,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19306cd40911a5ae8b4787c9c5d22ba2cef63b75","tid":625252,"uid":87688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"發霉定中毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a251d7f712d203847ef81e4cbddb82586e5ced","tid":625252,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"Ikea"},{"pid":"160c9718318f659c83e4c365bd04fb8e911c05c7","tid":625252,"uid":82121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0